{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-template-js","path":"/pages/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"9f50a3aa-2556-5142-8805-7fd3bcdc5240","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/72e01/aboutme.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/8ac56/aboutme.webp 240w,\n/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/d3be9/aboutme.webp 480w,\n/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/e46b2/aboutme.webp 960w,\n/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/a9a89/aboutme.webp 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/09b79/aboutme.jpg 240w,\n/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/7cc5e/aboutme.jpg 480w,\n/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/6a068/aboutme.jpg 960w,\n/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/72e01/aboutme.jpg 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/cf4ca9cecaf47a45076f9c1943d8cbc5/6a068/aboutme.jpg\"\n          alt=\"About\"\n          title=\"About\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"谷口-瑶光\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%B0%B7%E5%8F%A3-%E7%91%B6%E5%85%89\" aria-label=\"谷口 瑶光 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>谷口 瑶光</h2>\n<p><strong>Yoko TANIGUCHI</strong><br>\nWatercolor Artist, IT Engineer</p>\n<p>I was born in 1987, Japan. I started drawing and programming when I was a child.\nSince graduating from an university, I’ve been developing backbone systems of local governments and companies in the IT industry.\nCurrently I’m not only working as an engineer, but also producing watercolors as an artist. </p>\n<h3 id=\"deity-buddha-and-radiance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deity-buddha-and-radiance\" aria-label=\"deity buddha and radiance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Deity, Buddha and Radiance</h3>\n<p>My life theme is “Radiance”.  </p>\n<p>There are many difficulties in this world. I approach the problems by creating arts focus on Radiance.<br>\nThe main category is Watercolour. You can browse my work in the past on Instagram.<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yokotamanoko/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.instagram.com/yokotamanoko/</a><br>\nA gallery page on this site will be set up soon.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://forms.gle/HMVYyZf8vrsakRoC6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Contact Form</a></strong></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"About","date":null,"description":null,"socialImage":"/media/aboutme.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/pages/about/"}}}